#. <section class="sutta" id="sn1.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn1.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 1"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 1"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Naḷavagga"
msgstr "1. A Reed"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 3. Upanīyasutta → upanīyatisuttaṃ (bj, pts2) | upaneyyasuttaṃ (s1-3) | upaneyyaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn1.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Upanīyasutta"
msgstr "3. Led On"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.3:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn1.3:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho sā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr "Standing to one side, that deity recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.3:2.1"
msgid "“Upanīyati jīvitamappamāyu,"
msgstr "“This life, so very short, is led onward."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.3:2.2"
msgid "Jarūpanītassa na santi tāṇā;"
msgstr "There’s no shelter for someone who’s been led on by old age."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.3:2.3"
msgid "Etaṃ bhayaṃ maraṇe pekkhamāno,"
msgstr "Seeing this peril in death,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.3:2.4"
msgid "Puññāni kayirātha sukhāvahānī”ti."
msgstr "you should do good deeds that bring happiness.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.3:3.1"
msgid "“Upanīyati jīvitamappamāyu,"
msgstr "“This life, so very short, is led onward."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.3:3.2"
msgid "Jarūpanītassa na santi tāṇā;"
msgstr "There’s no shelter for someone who’s been led on by old age."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.3:3.3"
msgid "Etaṃ bhayaṃ maraṇe pekkhamāno,"
msgstr "Seeing this peril in death,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.3:3.4"
msgid "Lokāmisaṃ pajahe santipekkho”ti."
msgstr "one looking for peace would drop the world’s bait.”"
